pto industry, and pushes crypto out of the weird gray area it&#8217;s been =
forced to operate in. Entrepreneurs trying to build new things should under=
stand the rules of the road going in, and FIT21 is a step in that direction=
=2E There&#8217;s still a long way to g=
o &#8212; it will face headwinds in th=
e Senate &#8212; but it&#8217;s the second time in two weeks where crypto r=
eceived bipartisan support from the House. 71 Democrats, including financia=
l whiz kid Nancy Pelosi, voted for the bill. Crypto is becoming bipartisan.=
 </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Then yesterday, a double whammy! </p><p style=3D"col=
