k</a><span>, crypto provides the best set of tools we have to address chall=
enges with money and finance, and to </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com=
/redirect/79c289b8-b062-499c-9e58-378bdf05e0fc?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5=
T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55)=
