 lithium mine in the US - we&#8217;re net importers. The Department of Ener=
gy wants to produce all of our own lithium </span><a href=3D"https://substa=
ck.com/redirect/b298972d-068d-4e66-9009-c2189a863298?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ=
